   Brewer, C. Kenneth, US Forest Serv, Washington Off, Salt Lake City, UT USA.
   Brooks, Evan B., Virginia Polytech Inst \& State Univ, Blacksburg, VA 24061 USA.
   Gorelick, Noel, Google Corp, Menlo Pk, CA USA.
   Hernandez, Alexander J., Utah State Univ, Logan, UT 84322 USA.
   Huang, Chengquan, Univ Maryland, College Pk, MD 20742 USA.
   Loveland, Thomas R.; Vogelmann, James E.; Yang, Limin, US Geol Survey, Earth Resources Observat \& Sci Ctr, Sioux Falls, SD USA.
