Affiliation = {Anagnostou, EN (Corresponding Author), Univ Connecticut, Dept Civil \& Environm Engn, Storrs, CT 06269 USA.
   Bhuiyan, Md Abul Ehsan; Nikolopoulos, Efthymios, I; Anagnostou, Emmanouil N., Univ Connecticut, Dept Civil \& Environm Engn, Storrs, CT 06269 USA.},
