Affiliation = {Du, CW (Corresponding Author), Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Soil Sci, State Key Lab Soil \& Sustainable Agr, Nanjing 210008, Peoples R China.
   Du, CW (Corresponding Author), Univ Chinese Acad Sci, Coll Adv Agr Sci, Beijing 100049, Peoples R China.
   Ge, Haixiao; Ma, Fei; Li, Zhenwang; Du, Changwen, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Soil Sci, State Key Lab Soil \& Sustainable Agr, Nanjing 210008, Peoples R China.
