Affiliation = {Zhong, WX (Corresponding Author), Univ Georgia, Dept Stat, Athens, GA 30622 USA.
   Wang, F (Corresponding Author), Chinese Acad Med Sci, Beijing Hosp, Dept Cardiol, Natl Ctr Gerontol,Inst Geriatr Med, Beijing, Peoples R China.
