   Rose, Sherri, Harvard Med Sch, Dept Hlth Care Policy, Boston, MA USA.
   Spellman, Stephen R.; Lee, Stephanie J., Ctr Int Blood \& Bone Marrow Transplant Res, Minneapolis, MN USA.
   Verneris, Michael, Univ Colorado, Dept Med, Denver, CO USA.
   Hsu, Katharine C., Mem Sloan Kettering Canc Ctr, New York, NY USA.
   Fleischhauer, Katharina, Univ Hosp, Inst Expt Cellular Therapy, Essen, Germany.
   Lee, Stephanie J., Fred Hutchinson Canc Res Ctr, Seattle, WA USA.
   Abdi, Reza, Brigham \& Womens Hosp, Renal Div, Transplantat Res Ctr, Boston, MA USA.
   Abdi, Reza, Childrens Hosp, Boston, MA USA.},
DOI = {10.1371/journal.pone.0190610},
