   Ullah, Farhan, Northwestern Polytech Univ, Sch Software, Xian 710072, Shaanxi, Peoples R China.
   Jabbar, Sohail, Univ Faisalabad, Dept Computat Sci, Faisalabad 38000, Pakistan.},
DOI = {10.1142/S0218126622503029},
EarlyAccessDate = {JUL 2022},
Article-Number = {2250302},
Keywords = {Cybersecurity; android image; stacked ensemble; malware visualization;
   threats detection},
Author-Email = {hamadnaeemh@yahoo.com
