   Shi, Ying, China Stand Med Informat Res Ctr, Shenzhen, Peoples R China.
   Wang, Haibo, Sun Yat Sen Univ, Clin Trial Unit, Affiliated Hosp 1, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.},
