   Xu, Hanzeyu, Nanjing Normal Univ, Sch Geog, Nanjing 210023, Peoples R China.
   Liu, Aixia, Minist Nat Resources, Land Satellite Remote Sensing Applicat Ctr, Beijing 10048, Peoples R China.},
