Affiliation = {Liao, LD (Corresponding Author), Univ Calif Berkeley, Div Biostat, Berkeley, CA 94720 USA.
   Liao, Lauren D.; Hubbard, Alan E., Univ Calif Berkeley, Div Biostat, Berkeley, CA 94720 USA.
