Abstract = {The paper proposes a new GEP-based batch ensemble classifier constructed
   using the stacked generalization concept. In our approach combination of
   base classifiers involves evolving the meta-gene using genes induced by
   GEP from randomly generated combinations of instances with randomly
   selected subsets of attributes. The main property of the discussed
