   Le, Nguyen Quoc Khanh, Taipei Med Univ, Coll Med, Inserv Master Program Artificial Intelligence Med, Taipei 110, Taiwan.
   Le, Nguyen Quoc Khanh, Taipei Med Univ Hosp, Translat Imaging Res Ctr, Taipei 110, Taiwan.},
